Charlie

Jira Service Management, Server & Data Center{panel}

h3. Summary

The "From:" header format in notification emails do not match format specified in JIRA's General Configuration
h3. Steps to Reproduce
 # Go to JIRA's General Configuration page and check the *Email from* configuration. By Default this is {{${fullname} (JIRA)}}
 # Do something in a JIRA core project that would trigger a notification.
 # Go to the email client. You should see the From header of the notification something like {{John Doe (JIRA)}}}
 # Now go to a JIRA Service Desk project and then do an action that results in a notification
 # Go to the email client

h3. Expected Results

You would expect the From header of the notification to be something like {{John Doe (JIRA)}}}
h3. Actual Results

the From header of the notification email is simply {{John Doe}}

