Use case:
Service Desk currently requires an email configured for every Service Desk created. For Enterprise customers, their system can contain over 100 portals. This means creating a separate e-mail account and configuration for each portal. Maintaining all of these accounts can be quite time consuming.

In JIRA, it's possible to create a single handler for commenting into all projects, for example: Add Comments to Existing Tickets. This allows a single setup for every project. A single e-mail address.

